又一定贏<br />\n到最高法院都唔鳩理你， 又話美國法治已死全部收晒錢， 唔洗理法院喇<br />\n仲有faithless elector可以唔理投票結果而揀侵，不過原來又無喎全部electors都係賣國賊遲啲要清算<br />\n唔緊要仲有參議員最後可以推翻選舉人票結果， 點知最後得六君子支持其他GOP議員唔撐，rubio，graham， McConnell全部反骨仔，又要槍斃<br />\n屌唔驚仲有最後大佬彭斯可以推翻結果，哦原來佢先係終極大仆街未開會就講明唔會幫侵反cup<br />\n全部收晒錢deep state<br />\n都唔緊要我地仲有咩民兵組織發動內戰，殺晒民主黨左膠賣國賊，仲有軍隊都擁護侵，侵侵一定戰勝歸來<br />\n屌你老母我睇到真係笑到瀨屎，全世界錯晒佢啱晒， 成班精神病人<br />\n好文分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a35d1bd07c62f08f50f4429225be097ef68324f","tid":2358734,"uid":268591,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:51:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾低質post，拉！"},{"pid":"d7a1e15bcb4e07e122cbd68d59222e31025ec246","tid":2358734,"uid":279119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a35d1bd07c62f08f50f4429225be097ef68324f","tid":2358734,"uid":268591,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:51:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾低質post，拉！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"Block<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d51c7f40bf0e2ccfd2dcd91c5048669736d8bf4","tid":2358734,"uid":150483,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:54:55.000Z","msg":"樓主你又釣到4樓件cctoy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲通常兩邊吹"},{"pid":"403402f0838ffc61d7d73b85dab989749c21ee5d","tid":2358734,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ab0688d3d8b031b35fba4af71f8e8244584410c1","tid":2358734,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T10:42:45.000Z","msg":"面對現實啦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntrump輸左啦<br />\n連trump自己都跪你仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=